        "Cornstarch (approx. £1.00)",
        "Spring Onions (approx. £0.60)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Sichuan Steamed Silken Tofu with Spicy Beef Topping",
      "instructions": [
        "Place the whole block of silken tofu on a heatproof serving plate and steam for 8 minutes. Carefully drain off any excess water.",
        "Finely mince the garlic and ginger.",
        "Heat oil in a small pan, stir-fry the minced beef until crispy.",
        "Add the minced garlic, ginger, light soy sauce, chili oil, and Sichuan pepper oil to the beef, frying until aromatic.",
        "Pour the hot, spicy beef mixture directly over the steamed silken tofu.",
        "Garnish with chopped spring onions and toasted sesame seeds, then serve immediately."
      ],
      "required_ingredients": [
