      "instructions": [
        "Poach the chicken breasts in boiling water with a few slices of ginger and spring onion for 15 minutes until fully cooked. Let cool.",
        "Use a rolling pin or meat mallet to lightly beat the chicken breasts to loosen the fibers, then shred the meat by hand.",
        "Whisk the peanut butter with hot water, soy sauce, Chinkiang vinegar, sugar, and chili oil until smooth, sweet, savory, and pourable.",
        "Arrange the shredded chicken on a plate, scatter finely sliced spring onions over the top.",
        "Drizzle the rich, spicy peanut sauce generously over the chicken and serve cold or at room temperature."
      ],
      "required_ingredients": [
