        "Heat oil in a frying pan over medium-high heat. Add the chicken and cook until golden brown on all sides (about 5-6 minutes).",
        "Pour the sweet and savory peanut sauce directly into the pan, stirring constantly to coat the chicken as the sauce bubbles and caramelizes.",
        "Toss in the chopped spring onions, stir for another 30 seconds until wilted but vibrant, and serve with steamed rice."
      ],
      "required_ingredients": [
